GCAC1AU.original: ~z~It's a good thing you don't want to go out and kill people all the time. There might be some serious consequences to that.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~幸好你没有想着出门杀人，不然后果就很严重了。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~And that's because my life has so much in it and it's so much
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~因为我的人生非常丰富，比任何人

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~Yeah, work is sometimes hard to come by.
~z~But this other guy I was dating told me he'd invest and that I should and that I had a lot of talent and I think he's right.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~只是一个和我约过的人说会给我投资，那我就拍吧，反正我很有才华，他说的没错。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~Isn't that what you do quite often?
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~这不就是你平常做的事情吗？

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~the situation is weird. This is the twenty-first century. It's so now what we're doing.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~但就是感觉很奇怪。这就是21世纪，这就是我们的现状。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~I know. But it was also true and that's what this guy told me that I was dating last night.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~我知道，这话没错，昨晚跟我约会的那个男人也是这么说的。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~God, I've never thought of it that way.
~z~It fell through - but, to be honest, cinema is dead. I mean, it's so old fashioned.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~吹了。不过说实话，电影已死。这种载体过时了。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~I think bits of it, they are so beautiful and sad and... they make me cry.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~我略微想了想，它们太美好、太悲惨了...都让我哭出来了。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~I don't stop to think about what the consequences are.
~z~City life is weird, you know? Well, tell me about yourself.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~都市生活很怪，对吧？你介绍下自己吧。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~I really understand people so, they're drawn to me. I mean, that's what people who talk to me and read my blog feel.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~我真的很懂别人，所以他们都被我吸引了。这就是跟我聊天、读我博客的人的感受。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~Yeah... okay but I'd say that I'm a feminist. I think that every woman in this day and age should be.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~行，好吧...但我会说自己是女权主义者。现代女性都该支持女权。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~These days with all of the internet and videos and stuff and my blog and sites like electrictit.com and stuff -
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~现在网上有那么多视频和资源，还有我的博客和电子咪咪这样的网站，

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~I've never thought that writing my blog was "doing" something. It's just an extension of my personality. I'm creative.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~我从来没把写博客当成什么事。这只是我个性的延伸而已，我很有创造力的。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~I like variety. Anyway, did I tell you? I'm making a movie.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~各种口味我都会试试。对了，有跟你说过吗？我正在拍电影。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~I know. You're power. You're masculinity. You're freedom. In some ways, you're my muse.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~我知道。你就是力量，就是阳刚，就是自由。某种意义上，也是我的创作源泉。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~People really relate to me. They can take a bit of my life and see it as their own.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~人们真的很亲近我。他们可以品味我的人生，当成自己的一部分。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~I mean we don't need a man to help us get by in life. I do what I want, when I want and that's that.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~不需要男人帮我们维持温饱。我可以为所欲为，想做什么就做什么。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~They get this connection. It's like they feel this glow off me and my life and they want to be near me. I mean, do you feel that?
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~他们受我吸引。就好像能感受到我和我生活中的光芒，想要接近我。你感受到了吗？

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~Ha fucking ha... I've been really busy.
~z~Not like one of those idiot girls - I mean I know them they are all jealous of me because I'm an individual.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~我和那些白痴女不一样，我也知道她们都嫉妒我的特立独行。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~Niko, if you had to classify yourself, what would you be?
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~Niko，如果要给自己归类，你是哪种人？

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~Or a mouth, telling everyone who cares to listen about your life.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~或者说是嘴，可以向所有愿意倾听你的生活的人讲述。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~It's going to be amazing. It's going to be the great American novel, only a movie.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~拍出来一定很棒。这将是一部伟大的美国小说，只是以电影呈现。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~No doubt. Why are you so angry?
~z~It's good that you're happy in your home. My home was not so comfortable.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~能在老家幸福生活是件好事。我的老家就没那么舒服了。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~I've always kept diaries and, you know, thought really deep thoughts. I don't go in for all the bullshit... the trivial stuff.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~我一直在记日记，你也知道，还思考地很深入。我不会去管那些什么狗屁...没用的琐事。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~Nor did I... that was a joke. I wasn't planning to.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~我也没有...刚才是开玩笑的。我就没打算写书。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~That is so right. People need to hear about me. I really touch people.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~太对了，人们是得了解了解我。我真的很能打动别人。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~everything myself at Anna Rex spring/summer collection.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~买下Anna Rex店里春夏款的所有衣服。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~I don't know - I haven't written it yet.
~z~I don't believe in classifying people. I think it's what we do that makes us who we are, moment to moment.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~我不相信什么给人归类。个人的行为决定了我们的身份，向来如此。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~I don't know, because I can't get my shit together. Oh fuck it, it is together. I'm uh, it is together, sorry...
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~不知道，因为我他妈不大清醒。哦操，清醒了。我，呃，现在清醒了，抱歉。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~But I'm not an airhead. I mean I could be - I'm fun enough - but I'm also really intelligent.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~但我不是傻瓜。我确实能是，因为我够有趣，但我其实很聪明。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~I'm writing a novel which is going to be so much deeper than the stuff on the blog.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~我正在写小说，比我写的博客还要深刻。
~z~有一天我发现了这个博客网站。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~You cannot leave your apartment in this city without spending money so I guess you need to work.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~在这里出了家门就不可能不花钱，我想因此才需要工作。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~I don't think I'd get let into a college party or Maisonette 9.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~大学派对和9号豪宅我好像都去不了。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~Because I have these thoughts, yep, and I know they're important.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~因为我有各种想法，对，而且这些想法很重要。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~Everything... No, nothing. That's what dating is isn't it? Giving bits of information. Teasing people.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~我的一切...不，不告诉你。这就是约会，不是吗？ 只给很少的信息，挑逗对方。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~Listen, my life is not empty, jackass. It's amazing. I have crazy adventures.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~听着，我的生活并不空虚，蠢驴，它棒得很。我能经历疯狂的冒险。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~I was going through the stuff on www.blogsnobs.org and I realized that I had to get Alex Chilton out there.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~我看了www.blogsnobs.org上的各种内容，然后意识到得让我Alex Chilton为世人所知。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~It's about me. It started out as a blog, but it's evolved... into so much more than that. I mean sometimes,
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~是关于我的。本来想写成博客，但它变了...达到了远超博客的水平。有时候，

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~Tell me about it, I walk down the street.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~这还用你说。我经常出去逛街，

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~I mean, you're living it, Niko - you're an experience. you're not an intellectual. You don't care.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~你现在就在生活，Niko，活生生的例子。你没有什么才华，你不在乎。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~Really amazing thoughts, about people and the world and stuff.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~真的是很奇妙的想法，关于人与世界之类的。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~No. I'm liberated. I'm free. You can't control me, typical misogynist. Women can be artists too.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~不。我已经被解放了，我是自由的。你控制不了我，典型的仇女癌。女人也可以做艺术家。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~I had to expose my deepest thoughts to the public and that's when I created the Liberated Woman blog.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~我必须向大众展现最深刻的思考，于是就建立了「自由女性」这个博客。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~Oh, that's actually a quote that I've already used on my blog. What piece of my life do I want to show you first?
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~噢，那句话我在博客里用过了。先向你展示我生活的哪方面好呢？

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~I know what they want and what they're feeling. How is some professor going to be able to give me a grade on what I already know?
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~我知道他们的想法和感受。哪个教授能在我熟知的领域授予我学位呢？

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~It's not like I haven't been on a date like this before. I mean I've picked up guys on craplist and on dating sites but
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~我也不是第一次这样约人了。我在craplist和各种交友网站上约过很多人，

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~It's as much a part of me as an arm or a leg.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~现在它已经是我如同手足的一部分了。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~Oh, what would you know about this stuff?
~z~It must be so hard for you finding work and stuff in Liberty. I am told immigrants have a really hard time here.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~你在自由城找工作的时候一定很难吧。听说移民在这儿的日子不好过。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~Letting them see pieces of your life but not the whole picture.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~只让他们窥探你生活的局部而不是全部。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~Yes - I always knew I'd be a film maker. I have a very strong visual sense.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~确实，我一向认为自己会成为电影人。我的视觉设计能力很强。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~I mean, you know, I really understand people already.
~z~Oh he doesn't count. He's not a man. He's Daddy. I'll have any man I want to. Young, old, American, European. Like you,
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~哦，他不算。他不算是男人，他是爹地。我想找什么男人就找什么男人。小年轻、老头子、美国人、欧洲人。比如你。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~I mean, I'll do that myself and I won't rely on men to get me what I need.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~就是说，我自己就会这么做，不会等着男人送上来。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~I'm sorry. Man, we're going to have the best time.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~对不起。天。还是继续享受欢乐时光吧。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~I'm going to be famous. But not just for no reason, seriously.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~我会出名的，但不是无故出名，真的。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~I mean, some people from here have a tough time getting work too.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~我是说，就连美国本地人都有就业危机。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~The other day, I met this guy and I slept with him, and I wrote about it on my blog.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~有一天，我遇到了这个男人，和他睡了一觉，然后写到了博客里。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~I mean, I pick you up and I don't give a shit what my Mother will say, or what friends think.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~就是说，我约了你，就不会管我母亲逼逼些什么，也不管我的朋友怎么想。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~Doesn't your father pick up your credit card tabs?
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~你的信用卡不还是你爸在还吗？

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~So, Niko. Do you want to tell me about yourself? I cannot believe we're going on a date and we don't even know each other.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~那，Niko。你能介绍下自己吗？在互不了解的情况下约会不太现实。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~I was trying to figure out why it was that I related to you so easily. That must be it.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~我有想过为什么会这么轻易地就接近你。肯定就是这样。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~Well, that's not the point. I mean, yep, narrative is dead. It's done. It's all about living.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~那不重要。我是说，对，叙事已死，死透了。重要的是生活。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~Have you been reading my blog? It was really funny this week.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~你有没有在看我的博客？这周的更新超有趣的。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~I'm always fun. I'm a fun person.
~z~Next thing I know I've seen three pairs of shoes that I have to have and it's time to call Daddy and get the limit on my credit card extended.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~一出去就看上了三双鞋，反手就打给爹地让他提升我的信用卡额度了。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~But, mostly I'm my own muse. I mean, I'm going to be an important person. I think I'll change the world.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~一般我自己才是我的创作源泉。我会成为一个大人物，我以后会改变世界。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~Yes, he's amazing. But don't worry. Not all of the guys I date have to be intellectuals.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~对，他很棒。不过别担心，跟我约会的人也可以不是才子。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~richer and deeper than everyone else's. I mean, they relate to me because I'm better than them.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~都要丰富、深刻。我比他们强，他们才会亲近我。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~Not really what I meant. So, you got a fancy college degree that gets you noticed?
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~跟我说的不太一样。对了，你是不是有个引人瞩目的大学学位？

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~Anyway, the more stuff I do the more I have to write about in my blog... and I'll put it in my novel too.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~总之，我做的越多，在博客里写的就越多...放到我小说里的也越多。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~The thing about me is, I'm interesting. People feel like they can talk to me and open up.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~我这人吧，还挺有趣的。跟我聊天的人都会自然地敞开心扉。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~You think people are going to read this?
~z~So, this blog you write. Is that all you want to do?
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~那，你在写的这个博客，就是你想做的一切了吗？

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~Everyone tells me how creative I am. Especially men. Women are often jealous. You know how girls can be?
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~大家都说我很有想法，尤其是男人。女人就以嫉妒为主了。你知道女人能多嫉妒吗？

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~I don't know. I'm not from here. I'm trying to get through life in a strange country but it isn't easy.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~不好说。我不是本地人，还在尝试融入异国生活，但是有点困难。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~I mean, I will go out and order the most expensive thing on the menu. And I'll buy
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~出门吃饭我会点最贵的菜，还会给自己

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~Thanks... yep - I'm an intellectual. I mean, I haven't gotten going yet, but I am.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~谢了...对，我是个才女。虽然还不完全是，但也确实是。
~z~太他妈容易了。我可是艺术家。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~Oh, I write a thread called Liberated Woman on blogsnobs.org.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~噢，我在blogsnobs.org上开了一个叫「自由女性」的博客。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~College parties are just for losers who don't get let into Maisonette 9.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~大学派对是给进不了9号豪宅的失败者准备的。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~Some people make it difficult, yes? What do you want me to know about you?
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~总有人来找你麻烦，对吧？你想让我了解你的哪些方面？

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~I haven't had any trouble. It's not just because I've never had a paying job, because I'm an intellectual.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~我倒没遇上。不只是因为我从未上过班，也是因为我的才华。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~I'm from Middle Park West, I've never thought about leaving Liberty City.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~我来自中心公园西，从没想过要离开自由城。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~Okay well that's sick. You don't get what I'm saying. I mean -
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~那可太糟了。你没听懂我的意思，我是说，

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~He told me what was so amazing about my writing was that it was funny and tender and heartbreakingly original,
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~他告诉我我的文章妙就妙在趣味、柔情与令人心碎的真实经历，

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~Yeah, and I couldn't stand to be away from Liberty either.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~对，而且我的生活也离不开自由城。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~You live! You don't think! And that's beautiful.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~你活着！还不思考！实在太美妙了。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~I won't let consequences hold me back from the moment.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~后果是无法阻止我活在当下的。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~I went to college, I was going to be a psych. major but I found it too easy.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~我是上过大学，本来主修心理学的，不过我觉得这个太简单了。

GCAC1AU.original: ~z~Well, I've been blogging, and I've been doing a lot of web 2.0 shit. And I've... I've... well all kinds of crazy things.
GCAC1AU.translated: ~z~我在写博客，也整了一堆Web 2.0的玩意。而且还...还...总之啥都做了。
